<h2>Dubplate 0.2.3</h2>
<ul>
  <li><span class="t">Quality</span> &ldquo;Best&rdquo; is now the default for new splits &mdash; ensemble acapellas and cascaded full stems out of the box.</li>
  <li><span class="t">Welcome</span> The empty queue now walks you through drop &rarr; process &rarr; export, with format notes built in.</li>
  <li><span class="t">Installer</span> The download is a proper drag-to-Applications window &mdash; no more read-me file.</li>
  <li><span class="t">Updates</span> Release notes now appear right here instead of a web page, and Dubplate checks for updates daily on its own.</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
